Package: bamlssGP
Title: Gaussian Process Responses for the bamlss Package
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: as.person("Hannes Riebl <hriebl@uni-goettingen.de> [aut, cre]")
Description: This package implements different Gaussian processes as response
    distribution families for the bamlss package, i.e. for Bayesian additive
    models for location, scale, and shape. It also provides an efficient MCMC
    sampler for these models.
Imports: bamlssAPI, purrr, rlang
Suggests: bamlss, numDeriv, testthat
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
